title: Iowa forces 4 turnovers, tops No. 19 Wisconsin 10-6
text:
> Sports Iowa forces 4 turnovers, tops No. 19 Wisconsin 10-6 Iowa's Drew Ott (95), Macon Plewa (42) and Nate Meier carry the Heartland Trophy after their 10-6 win over Wisconsin in an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Madison, Wis. (AP Photo/Morry Gash)
